Package: uwebsockets-dev
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: libusockets-dev (>= 0.8.8),
         libuv1-dev,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight C++ WebSocket library
 uWebSockets is a simple to use, yet thoroughly optimized implementation
 of WebSocket and HTTP protocols for C++. It provides both client and
 server implementations with support for SSL/TLS and HTTP/3.
 .
 This is a header-only library package containing development files.

